reviews.text:
Isn't my favorite flavor profile, but this adds a darkness most blue raspberries do not have. It's not a slushie type, it's not a freezepop, it's more like picking a fresh raspberry off the vine (Tree? How do raspberries grow?) in some mystical world that actually grows blue colored raspberries. &#xD;
I plan on using this mix in some weird profiles eventually.&#xD;
Great job!
